Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_all_reg..._is_macro_cell(25.10)  timing_all_reg..._is_macro_cell(25.10)

Name
       timing_all_registers_identify_macros_include_is_macro_cell

Syntax
       timing_all_registers_identify_macros_include_is_macro_cell    {true   |
       false}

       Default: true

       Enables to include cells as macro cells.

       When set to true, the software includes cells as  macro  cells  if  the
       is_macro_cell  property  (see  get_property)  is set to true in the li-
       brary.

       When set to false, the all_registers command will not return cells  for
       which the is_macro_cell property is true.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

